   Campus
   10/30/18

Advisory Committee supports Platztor Campus

   The Advisory Committee is supporting the planned Platztor Campus site
   of the University of St.Gallen and the construction plans amounting to
   207 million francs. The Platztor Campus site will enable the
   sustainable development of the University of St.Gallen and create
   urgently needed teaching and research facilities for basic education.
   Damian Borth in "Forbes"
