   Events
   09/19/19
   City with night lights
   >

Smart Government Day 2019

A current study shows how leaders from politics and administration can
promote "Smart Government”. The results will be presented at the Smart
Government Day on 24 September 2019. Vitali Klitschko, Mayor of Kiev, will
give a talk on Smart City Kiev.

   People
   08/29/19
   Carla del Ponte talking to Ignazio Cassis
   >

Carla Del Ponte wins award for her uncompromising pursuit of war criminals

Carla del Ponte was recently awarded the Erich Walser Generation Prize at the
University of St.Gallen. The Ticino-born lawyer received the prize in
recognition of her services as chief prosecutor for war crimes committed in
former Yugoslavia and Rwanda.

