   02/08/19

AACSB accreditation until to 2023

   The Association to Advance Collegiate Schools of Business (AACSB) has
   renewed the accreditation of the University of St.Gallen (HSG) for the
   next five years. HSG is one of four universities in Switzerland and 831
   worldwide to bear this quality seal.
