Swiss Federal Council elections: No content please!

Fundamental political issues seem to barely play a role in the public debate
surrounding the Swiss Federal Council elections, to be held on 5 December
2018. Patrick Emmenegger, Professor of Political Science at the University of
St.Gallen (HSG), paints a picture of the current mood.

